
  Design Benefits of Implementation

  1. Shallow Traversal (depth=1) - Fast Intelligence

  # Quick impact check - only immediate relationships
  impact = await choices_service.analyze_choice_impact(choice_uid, depth=1)
  # Returns: Direct goals, direct principles only
  # Performance: ~10-50ms (minimal graph traversal)

  2. Medium Traversal (depth=2) - Default Intelligence

  # Standard depth - 2-hop neighborhood
  impact = await choices_service.analyze_choice_impact(choice_uid, depth=2)  # Default
  # Returns: Goals → Supporting tasks, Principles → Guided goals
  # Performance: ~50-200ms (typical use case)

  3. Deep Traversal (depth=3-5) - Comprehensive Analysis

  # Full impact analysis - multi-hop cascading effects
  impact = await choices_service.analyze_choice_impact(choice_uid, depth=5)
  # Returns: Complete cascade chain (choice → goals → tasks → knowledge → learning paths)
  # Performance: ~200-1000ms (expensive but comprehensive)

